id: jf-wmc1
title: Publish same-day calendar patches with an explicit npm dist-tag
description: The first same-day ordinal tag was safely rejected before publication because npm treats YYYY.M.D-N as a SemVer prerelease and requires an explicit dist-tag.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: automation,bin,npm,regression,release
created_at: "2026-07-21T18:38:40.657Z"
